Lucy Doraine https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lucy_Doraine 0 Lucy Doraine (22 May 1898 – 14 October 1989) was a Hungarian film actress of the silent era. Born as Ilona Kovács in Budapest, she appeared in 24 films between 1918 and 1931. She was married to film director Michael Curtiz from 1918 to 1923. She died in Los Angeles, California, aged 91.
